A very different photo from that of the meeting between US President and Ukrainian President at the White House, where Trump found and Zelensky was clearly on the defensive, with his arms stuck on the body almost to protect himself: "The posture of the bodies makes us think that this time there was a constructive dialogue. The two look in the eyes, they're one in front of each other, and they look like prosthetics to each other. In the image I saw there's Zelensky talking, and Trump listening carefully with his hands on his feet"
